    "# pdf_docs = pdf_loader.load()\n",
    "# print(f\"Loaded {len(pdf_docs)} pages.\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Summary – Day 3 Completed ✅\n",
    "\n",
    "You have learned:\n",
    "- Loading documents with LangChain loaders (TextLoader, PyPDFLoader)\n",
    "- Splitting into overlapping chunks\n",
    "- Generating embeddings (OpenAI or HuggingFace)\n",
    "- Storing vectors in Pinecone\n",
    "- Similarity search queries\n",
    "\n",
    "**Next:** Day 4 – Advanced RAG (hybrid search, re-ranking, evaluation)\n",
    "\n",
    "Save this notebook and commit to your repository."
   }
  ]
